          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Sanitation Service Authority includes four engineering infrastructure items (even though often only the first one is strongly associated with the term \"sanitation\"): Excreta management systems, wastewater management systems (included here are wastewater treatment plants), solid waste management systems, drainage systems for rainwater, also called storm water drainage.",
